title: Monsoon (Preston School of Industry album)
text:
Monsoon is <a href="Preston%20School%20of%20Industry%20%28band%29">Preston School of Industry's</a> second and final album. It includes guest appearances by <a href="Wilco">Wilco</a> members and <a href="Scott%20McCaughey">Scott McCaughey</a>.
Critical reception.
"Monsoon" received mixed reviews from critics. On <a href="Metacritic">Metacritic</a>, the album holds a score of 62/100 based on 21 reviews, indicating "generally favorable reviews."
Track listing.
All music & lyrics by <a href="Scott%20Kannberg">Spiral Stairs</a>.
